title: BRIEF-Morphosys AG Says ‍Files Registration Statement In United States For A Proposed American Depositary Shares (ADS) Offering​
text: March 22, 2018 / 7:03 PM / Updated 25 minutes ago BRIEF-Morphosys AG Says ‍Files Registration Statement In United States For A Proposed American Depositary Shares (ADS) Offering​ Reuters Staff March 22 (Reuters) - Morphosys Ag: * SAYS ‍FILES REGISTRATION STATEMENT IN UNITED STATES FOR A PROPOSED AMERICAN DEPOSITARY SHARES (ADS) OFFERING​ * SAYS ‍FINAL NUMBER OF ADSS TO BE OFFERED AND PRICE FOR OFFERING HAVE NOT YET BEEN DETERMINED​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
